# Package Manager: Bun

This project uses **bun** as the package manager. Always use `bun` commands, never `npm` or `yarn`.

```bash
# ✅ GOOD
bun install
bun add <package>
bun add -d <package>
bun remove <package>
bun run <script>

# ❌ BAD
npm install
npm install <package>
yarn add <package>
```

Lock file is `bun.lock` (not `package-lock.json`).
